tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE market_data (
  vendor_id INT,
  vendor_name VARCHAR(255),
  data_type VARCHAR(100),
  data_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  data_value DECIMAL(18, 2),
  PRIMARY KEY (vendor_id)
);

CREATE TABLE FinancialData (
	data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	vendor_id INT,
	data_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
	data_value DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
	FOREIGN KEY (vendor_id) REFERENCES MarketDataVendors(vendor_id)
);

CREATE TABLE ClientFinancialData (
	client_id INT,
	data_id INT,
	sale_date DATE,
	FOREIGN KEY (client_id) REFERENCES Clients(client_id),
	FOREIGN KEY (data_id) REFERENCES FinancialData(data_id)
);

CREATE TABLE financial_data (
    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    data_type VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    data_value DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    vendor_id INT,
    client_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE financial_data (
    data_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    vendor_id UUID REFERENCES market_data_vendors(vendor_id),
    data_name STRING NOT NULL,
    data_value DECIMAL,
    data_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE subscription (
    subscription_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    client_id UUID REFERENCES client_data(client_id),
    data_id UUID REFERENCES financial_data(data_id),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);
